        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Estimation cross-checked with industry information: The total shipment of corrugated board in Europe in 2021 was 28019000000 kg (https://www.fefco.org/sites/default/files/documents/Fefco_AnnualEvaluation_2021_0.pdf, last accessed March 2023). This amount corresponds to 72 % of the 38947712000 kg of “case materials” produced in Europe in 2021 (FAOSTAT http://www.fao.org/faostat/en/#data/FO)
The same share is applied to global production volume of "case materials, i.e., it is assumed that 72 % of the 183685954000 kg of global “case material” production consist of corrugated board (FAOSTAT http://www.fao.org/faostat/en/#data/FO),</productionVolumeComment>
